svg.text: Then with a huff and a puff I blow them away.And …poof… they’re gone, they cannot stay. Let me try said Inara as she held on to the stone … and with three deep breaths she started.

svg.text: I won’t know my friends,they won’t know me,I will be sad and tired,I will be lonelyI may get lost,I will be scaredI wont know anything,I am un-prepared She said.
